{"tid":641343,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺學術台好撚多痴線佬","createTime":"2018-04-25T02:43:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-25T03:24:21.000Z","uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6d4afa3379b8937e21dbe2bc7e52d3728ef19f43","tid":641343,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T02:43:31.000Z","msg":"本少一向喺感情台出沒，諗住入下其他台望下啦，點知一入學術台就中伏了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果要比喻就好似一個屋邨商場開左個學術研討咁。啲人係咁用英文覆post, 講啲望落好似有深度嘅句子，但係其實根本就唔係logical嘅嘢，拋左一下書包又唔會解釋下自己句嘢係點解，懶係凝造一鼓好玄嘅氣氛咁，一種你唔明係因為你唔夠能力理解嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。但係明明自己本身英文都唔好，又要用英文覆去自製一種好高學問嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。 跟住就有成堆人俾個痴線佬帶到離晒題，一個post可以轉十幾個topic, 成個精神分裂咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結論：一堆無學識嘅阿叔坐埋一齊扮晒勁抽嘢咁吹水"},{"pid":"40e87b68b36a681e4220c933e5ce3074867b6e4e","tid":641343,"uid":139676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T02:45:54.000Z","msg":"包括你？"},{"pid":"2c986e11d1a8202396c7d030f709530a1ca0ef4c","tid":641343,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40e87b68b36a681e4220c933e5ce3074867b6e4e","tid":641343,"uid":139676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T02:45:54.000Z","msg":"包括你？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T02:47:43.000Z","msg":"it's not the truth that makes you wise, it's the ignorace that makes you wise"},{"pid":"23bb909e5e1dbf65ee670f1e3c5123f2dfad305d","tid":641343,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T02:47:59.000Z","msg":"主流連登仔係ive仔<br />\n<br />\n好正常啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2adbe92d3936d338df532ad0dc7609882323318","tid":641343,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"23bb909e5e1